ConocoPhillips Reports Flaring, Power Loss at Illinois Refinery

-- B y   G r a n t   S m i t h
-- 
2011-03-17T08:27:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-17/conocophillips-reports-flaring-power-loss-at-illinois-refinery.html
  ConocoPhillips (COP)  said it flared gas
at its refinery in Roxana,  Illinois , after a  power failure ,
according to a filing with state regulators.  The incident occurred on March 15 at 1:02 p.m. local time,
according to a filing made with the Illinois Emergency
Management Agency.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Grant Smith in London at 
 gsmith52@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
